were always together.

790
00:43:59,320 --> 00:44:00,360
总是
Always.

791
00:44:21,840 --> 00:44:23,720
不 这张不要看
Oh, no, you don't want to look at that one.

792
00:44:24,000 --> 00:44:25,000
这是你吗
Is that you?

793
00:44:28,600 --> 00:44:29,600
是的
Yes.

794
00:44:32,160 --> 00:44:33,360
你当时多大
How old were you?

795
