My research colleagues.

801
00:44:51,560 --> 00:44:52,720
研究什么
For what?

802
00:44:52,880 --> 00:44:54,680
当然是数学
Mathematics, of course.

803
00:44:55,440 --> 00:44:57,040
真的吗
Really?

804
00:44:58,920 --> 00:45:00,520
好棒
Cool!

805
00:45:03,080 --> 00:45:04,840
那你后来
So, then you came to work...

806
00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:06,160
就来美国大学工作了?
at a college in America?

807
00:45:06,720 --> 00:45:07,760
不是
No.

808
00:45:07,920 --> 00:45:10,650
我嫁给了你外公
I married your grandfather...

809
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:13,160
跟他一起回到美国
