00:45:24,120 --> 00:45:25,840
你明天还有重要的事
You've got a big day tomorrow.

815
00:45:26,000 --> 00:45:28,970
来 起来
Come on. Up, up, up.

816
00:45:29,160 --> 00:45:30,490
