00:46:20,920 --> 00:46:23,490
照抄原题 谢谢
Exactly as written. Thank you.

831
00:46:28,840 --> 00:46:31,440
要让我看什么数学题
So, what's this problem I'm supposed to look at?

832
00:46:31,520 --> 00:46:33,320
不知道
I don't know.

833
00:46:33,480 --> 00:46:35,760
就像妈妈研究的那些问题吗
Is it like the problems Mom worked on?

834
00:46:35,920 --> 00:46:38,080
你妈研究的不是一些问题
Your mother didn't work on problems.

835
00:46:38,240 --> 00:46:40,400
她只研究了一个问题
She worked on just one problem.

836
00:46:40,560 --> 00:46:42,320
就一个吗
Just one?

837
00:46:42,480 --> 00:46:44,050
研究了一辈子
Her entire life?

838
00:46:44,200 --> 00:46:45,920
大部分
Most of it.

839
00:46:46,080 --> 00:46:47,280
看
Look.

840
