这些都是千年难题
These are the Millennium Problems.

841
00:46:52,840 --> 00:46:56,240
七个意义重大的难题
Seven great and meaningful problems.

842
00:46:56,400 --> 00:46:58,480
有些数学家
Some mathematicians have worked

843
00:46:58,560 --> 00:47:00,440
用了一辈子时间来证明
their entire lives to prove them.

844
00:47:01,200 --> 00:47:02,770
这个大胡子是谁
Who's the dude with the beard?

845
00:47:02,960 --> 00:47:04,370
他可不是普通人
That's not a dude.

846
00:47:04,520 --> 00:47:06,760
