That's Grigori Perelman.

847
00:47:06,920 --> 00:47:09,440
他证明了庞加莱猜想
He proved the Poincaré conjecture.

848
00:47:09,600 --> 00:47:12,680
七个问题中唯一一个得到证明的
The only one of the seven proved.

849
00:47:12,840 --> 00:47:14,440
这个
This...

850
00:47:16,320 --> 00:47:18,520
这是你妈研究的问题
This is your mother's problem.

851
00:47:19,760 --> 00:47:20,840
纳维…
Na... vi...

852
00:47:21,000 --> 00:47:23,730
纳维尔-斯托克斯方程
Navier-Stokes.

853
00:47:25,440 --> 00:47:27,240
没照片啊
No picture.

854
00:47:27,400 --> 00:47:29,240
- 她没证明吗 - 没有
- She didn't solve it? - No.

855
00:47:30,320 --> 00:47:31,730
她当时快证明出来了
She was close.

856
00:47:33,120 --> 00:47:35,000
她本来可以获得菲尔茨奖
She would have won the Fields Medal...

857
00:47:35,680 --> 00:47:37,560
