and probably shared a Nobel...

858
00:47:37,720 --> 00:47:40,080
因为在物理学上也有重要意义
considering what it would have meant for physics.

859
00:47:40,240 --> 00:47:43,130
也许将来我的照片也能挂在上面
Maybe I'll have my picture up here someday.

860
00:47:49,240 --> 00:47:51,000
如果你真的想
If you really desire it...

861
00:47:51,160 --> 00:47:53,890
你可以把你的照片挂在上面 孩子
you can have your picture there, darling.

862
00:47:54,040 --> 00:47:56,320
我可以帮你
I can help you.

863
00:47:56,480 --> 00:48:00,240
这需要专注和刻苦 但如果你成功了
It takes focus and hard work, but if you succeed...

864
00:48:01,320 --> 00:48:04,130
