00:49:22,360 --> 00:49:24,520
首先
Well, for starters,

892
00:49:24,600 --> 00:49:26,760
他忘了加上指数前的负号
he forgot the negative sign on the exponent.

893
00:49:26,920 --> 00:49:29,000
后面就讲不通了
It went downhill from there.

894
00:49:29,160 --> 00:49:30,730
这道题没法解
The problem was unsolvable.

