But I don't wanna live with her.

921
00:51:57,840 --> 00:51:59,000
她很专横
She's bossy.

922
00:52:00,320 --> 00:52:02,360
这话我听过
I've heard that.

923
00:52:02,720 --> 00:52:04,050
喂
Hey.

924
00:52:05,080 --> 00:52:07,730
