Promise?

926
00:52:13,960 --> 00:52:15,290
我保证
I promise.

927
00:52:15,480 --> 00:52:17,520
嗨 玛丽 我叫帕特戈尔丁
Hi, Mary. I'm Pat Golding,

928
00:52:17,600 --> 00:52:19,000
