Do you know why you're here?

931
00:52:22,800 --> 00:52:25,120
有人说过是为了什么事吗
I mean has anyone told you what this is about?

932
00:52:25,280 --> 00:52:26,840
我外婆希望我跟她一起住
My grandmother wants me to live with her

933
00:52:26,880 --> 00:52:28,160
而我想跟弗兰克一起住
and I wanna stay with Frank.

934
00:52:28,320 --> 00:52:30,240
很好
That's correct.

935
00:52:30,400 --> 00:52:32,600
