00:52:32,680 --> 00:52:34,520
你担心过吗
Does any of it worry you?

937
00:52:34,680 --> 00:52:37,650
不担心 弗兰克说我哪儿也不去
Nope. Frank says I'm not goin' anywhere.

938
00:52:38,560 --> 00:52:40,360
你舅舅说你哪儿都不去
Your uncle told you you're not going anywhere?

939
00:52:40,480 --> 00:52:42,240
15分钟之前说的
Just 15 minutes ago.

940
00:52:42,320 --> 00:52:43,360
我们谈完了吗
So, we done here?

941
00:52:44,960 --> 00:52:46,370
还没有
Not quite yet.

942
00:52:46,880 --> 00:52:49,280
除了弗兰克和弗雷德 我最好的朋友就是罗伯塔
My best friend other than Frank and Fred is Roberta...

