00:53:15,360 --> 00:53:17,520
但我喜欢海绵宝宝
But I got hooked on SpongeBob.

956
00:53:17,680 --> 00:53:19,640
主要是因为罗伯塔喜欢
Mostly because Roberta loves it.

957
00:53:21,560 --> 00:53:24,600
对了 我们周六晚上会看UFC
Oh. And on Saturday nights, we watch the UFC.

958
00:53:24,800 --> 00:53:26,760
UFC? 是不是…
The UFC? Is that...

