1620
01:29:55,920 --> 01:29:57,280
这不是完整的证明
It is not a completed proof...

1621
01:29:57,440 --> 01:30:00,090
- 是 - 这不是 不可能
- It is. - No! It isn't! It can't be.

1622
01:30:00,240 --> 01:30:01,480
伊芙琳 别说了
Evelyn, stop!

1623
01:30:03,040 --> 01:30:04,530
我要带走玛丽 抚养她
I'm taking Mary and I'm raising her

1624
01:30:04,600 --> 01:30:06,120
以我认为黛安所希望的方式
how I believe Diane would've wanted.

1625
01:30:06,280 --> 01:30:07,490
- 这由不得你 - 我知道…
- We'll see about that later. - I realize...

1626
01:30:07,520 --> 01:30:08,850
她不是普通人
she's not normal.

