Diane didn't always think things through.

1659
01:32:32,640 --> 01:32:33,840
我先出去了
I'll be outside.

1660
01:32:35,000 --> 01:32:36,330
你决定之后告诉我一声
Let me know what you wanna do.

1661
01:33:56,800 --> 01:33:57,890
这里是
You've reached

