1674
01:34:31,400 --> 01:34:32,600
是的
Uh, yes.

1675
01:34:35,280 --> 01:34:37,040
尚克兰博士
Doctor Shankland.

1676
01:34:37,560 --> 01:34:39,720
对不起 我听不清
I'm really sorry. I can't hear you.

1677
01:34:39,880 --> 01:34:41,720
你能大点声吗
Could you speak up, please?

1678
01:34:44,760 --> 01:34:45,800
喂
Hello?

1679
01:34:49,680 --> 01:34:52,040
我是伊芙琳阿德勒
Evelyn Adler...

1680
01:34:52,200 --> 01:34:54,120
我找西摩尚克兰
for Seymore Shankland, please.

1681
01:34:56,160 --> 01:34:57,410
你们要注意的是
And what I want you to notice,

1682
01:34:57,440 --> 01:34:58,880
当通过N计算P时
is that when you compute P of N...

1683
01:34:59,040 --> 01:35:00,960
